cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves collaborative representation and classification, which are also relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments involve face and scene images, which are commonly studied in multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
